The '''Prix de la Photographie, Paris''' or '''Px3''' is a European [[photography]] award. It was founded in 2007 and includes a Gold Award, Silver Award and Bronze Award.<ref>[http://www.photocompetitions.com/contests/prix-de-la-photographie-paris-px3/ 2015 Prix de la Photographie, Paris (Px3)]</ref><ref>[http://www.tomdjones.com/en/media/news/px3-gold-silver-award-2014 PX3 Gold & Silver award 2014]</ref><ref>[http://www.patriziaburra.com/Awards.html Awards]</ref>
Winning photographs from the competition are exhibited in a gallery in Paris and published in an annual book.
